ref:_00D7091pB._500Q000LtFDf:ref

Good morning.

We have activated an external access to our server so that you can 
export the configuration that previously existed on your server. 
Currently the user is not active, let me know when it would be 
convenient for you to establish a call through teams for it. This week 
we could establish the meeting from 14:10 hours to 15 hours. Next week I 
would have to look at the schedule. I look forward to your availability.

Steps to access the server:

1.- Access to the link "aru.gdaservicios.es". Accept the certificate and 
it will show you the login screen.

2.- You can access with the user: unetwrix and password:N3twr1x25! and 
you should see the following screen

3.- Click on the link of the equipment and you must download and install 
the launcher of pulse secure, to show the window of connection to the 
equipment by rdp. Once installed, click again and the login window will 
appear.

4.- Indicate in user: gdaunetwrix and password: to access the system.

5.- Here you will be inside a computer ready to access the server, where 
you will only have to click on the enabled icon on the desktop.

Best Regards.
